.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/china/gncj/2018-04-22/detail-ifznefkh7630184.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2Fchina%2Fgncj%2F2018-04-22%2Fdetail-ifznefkh7630184.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=OKkKX4yRVxIvfeGBdKyXJdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6b7dbad6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/china/gncj/2018-04-22/detail-ifznefkh7630184.d.html?from=wap</a></span><br />\n<br />\n由此可見，法律和規則的意義，它的演進邏輯是：<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">1、犯不上為了庇護一條魚而污染一條河；2、法律應該捍衛的本該是河流，而不是其中任何一種魚或一條魚；3、魚類是否繁榮不是法律該考慮的內容；4、河流乾淨了，魚類自然就繁榮了；5、縱容某條魚犯錯，它就會演變成最大的污染源。</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n美國一直就是這麼做的：並非針對具體的企業下狠手或庇護，而是一直捍衛法律和經濟環境這條河流。歷史上的案例太多了：同樣是波音牽頭成立的「聯合飛機與運輸」公司，1934年就被乾翻了；洛克菲勒和AT&amp;T，因涉嫌壟斷被拆分過多少次？"},{"pid":"7495257c66ab2194c6bbecdebadfa19629dcbdd6","tid":642180,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"你想要負皮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cbf062bcff3fe4be6b3f7c33a1a3c66015b9a0","tid":642180,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:16:56.000Z","msg":"唔抵得？？？"},{"pid":"969c4405c1737c5e410cfe2daf3f85de64572507","tid":642180,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"其實豐田寶係柒左wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己都承認係設計有問題"},{"pid":"dfbb29f382cd22fc60decb9cecab9ef5994aa7b7","tid":642180,"uid":77257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:19:08.000Z","msg":"同意標題<br />\n但內文例子全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccb17e0093ea5d66e6e7fd7234b168be